skdetail:

Invocation Name: ranch sounds
des: Giddyup! Transport yourself to a beautiful ranch soundscape. Get started by saying, 'Alexa, open Ranch Sounds,' and enjoy a 30-minute session of sound. It's an excellent feature to use during sleep, for deep relaxation, meditation practices, or to help concentrate on your tasks.
